  <chapter>
    <title>Documentation.</title>

    <section>
      <title>Identification.</title>

      <para>All documents are to be uniquely numbered.</para>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Correspondence.</title>

      <para>All correspondence documents to be stored/prepared in Microsoft
      Outlook Message (.msg) or plain ASCII text (.txt) format and to be
      uniquely numbered by the following numbering scheme:</para>

      <para>"work/xx_${unit_name}/documentation/yyyymmdd_${description}.ext"</para>

      <para>Where:</para>

      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>xx</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>unit number.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>yyyy</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>year number.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>mm</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>month number.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>dd</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>day number.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>ext</term>

          <listitem>
            <para>file extension.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Specifications.</title>

      <para>All specification documents to be prepared in e<emphasis
      role="bold">X</emphasis>tensible <emphasis role="bold">M</emphasis>arkup
      <emphasis role="bold">L</emphasis>anguage format (.xml), and to be
      uniquely numbered by the following numbering scheme:</para>

      <para>"work/xx_${unit_name}/documentation/xx_${description}.ext"</para>

      <para>Where:<variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>xx</term>

            <listitem>
              <para>unit number.</para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>

          <varlistentry>
            <term>ext</term>

            <listitem>
              <para>file extension.</para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
        </variablelist></para>
    </section>
  </chapter>

